title: Caitlyn and Vi are your Ocean Week reinforcements!
body:
Voting has closed and Caitlyn and Vi are your winners!

http://i.imgur.com/3hahQ0q.png

They will be on free rotation during Ocean Week and you will also be able to earn points towards the Ocean Week goals by winning games with them!

replies.body: Of course the cops would show up to help maintain order XD
Where is El Tigre Braum though??? D: Said he was available earlier today but he is still unavailable when i go to the store.
Why no Miss Fortune in ocean week? {{champion:21}} is sad.
I have both of them rito why

Yes, because Riot staff used hundreds of accounts to put Cait and Vi in first place.

Think about things before you post them.
